articles.title: Far-left activist convicted in executions of 2 FBI agents headed to parole hearing with support from Dems - Fox News
articles.description: The FBI Agents Association opposes parole for Leonard Peltier, the Native American activist who gunned down two FBI agents, Ronald Williams and Jack Coler, in 1975.
